3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) channels, which are commonly used in multimedia communication systems. 
4. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper deals with beamforming and power allocation, which are signal processing techniques commonly used in wireless communication systems. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with wireless communication systems, which are a topic in networking and internet architecture.
